795
00:47:01,467 --> 00:47:03,700
you brain to brain,
but at the same time,

796
00:47:03,700 --> 00:47:05,934
there's complete
distance and anonymity.

797
00:47:05,934 --> 00:47:08,834
So that's what led me
to the subject matter

798
00:47:08,834 --> 00:47:12,567
and the treatment
of Sexual Healing.

799
00:47:12,567 --> 00:47:18,834
Also, what I wanted to do
was create a real closeness,

800
00:47:18,834 --> 00:47:21,533
and I wanted the
audience to really care

801
00:47:21,533 --> 00:47:24,467
about the relationship
between these two characters

802
00:47:24,467 --> 00:47:28,400
who never meet in person until
the very end of the film.

803
00:47:28,400 --> 00:47:31,400
And my hope was that producers
and studios would say,

804
00:47:31,400 --> 00:47:32,000
wait a minute.

805
00:47:32,000 --> 00:47:34,567
This guy got us to care about
two people who were never

806
00:47:34,567 --> 00:47:37,433
even in the same
room, and so maybe we

807
00:47:37,433 --> 00:47:39,000
