831
00:48:46,967 --> 00:48:48,967
You could go on the
festival circuit, of course,

832
00:48:48,967 --> 00:48:50,700
but you don't make
any money doing that.

833
00:48:50,700 --> 00:48:54,033
So some people wondered, was it
a trick, a gimmick, et cetera?

834
00:48:54,033 --> 00:48:56,400
But I had this feeling
that if we pulled it off,

835
00:48:56,400 --> 00:48:58,266
somehow there would
be a market for it

836
00:48:58,266 --> 00:49:01,500
and we would be able to raise
money for the Minority AIDS

837
00:49:01,500 --> 00:49:02,033
Project.

838
00:49:02,033 --> 00:49:05,200
And so that's how I set it up,
and we were off and running.

839
00:49:11,767 --> 00:49:14,600
In the early stages
of preproduction,

840
00:49:14,600 --> 00:49:17,433
I had two actors who were
working with me in the two

841
00:49:17,433 --> 00:49:18,400
lead roles.

842
00:49:18,400 --> 00:49:20,233
Both of them were
friends of mine.

843
00:49:20,233 --> 00:49:24,033
