844
00:49:24,033 --> 00:49:27,133
And one of them,
the male lead, I

845
00:49:27,133 --> 00:49:29,567
ended up having a big
creative disagreement with.

846
00:49:29,567 --> 00:49:32,367
And he quit, or I
fired him, or both.

847
00:49:32,367 --> 00:49:33,667
I'm not sure.

848
00:49:33,667 --> 00:49:36,533
And the other one
decided to stay on,

849
00:49:36,533 --> 00:49:38,767
but we had to find
a new male lead.

850
00:49:38,767 --> 00:49:40,467
