863
00:50:04,967 --> 00:50:05,867
We were all set to go.

864
00:50:05,867 --> 00:50:07,500
What were we going to do?

865
00:50:07,500 --> 00:50:09,100
But it turned out to
be an opportunity,

866
00:50:09,100 --> 00:50:13,533
