867
00:50:13,533 --> 00:50:16,867
best friends, who he'd
known for years and years,

868
00:50:16,867 --> 00:50:18,500
was Helen Hunt.

869
00:50:18,500 --> 00:50:20,734
And I asked him,
very tentatively,

870
00:50:20,734 --> 00:50:22,233
if he would ask her.

871
00:50:22,233 --> 00:50:23,100
He did.

872
00:50:23,100 --> 00:50:26,266
She loved the role and
