886
00:51:03,767 --> 00:51:08,700
The first challenge I had in
working skillfully with actors

887
00:51:08,700 --> 00:51:13,033
on a set was when Helen
came to me about one

888
00:51:13,033 --> 00:51:16,633
of the scenes that had her doing
