to kind of make

891
00:51:21,433 --> 00:51:23,800
a fool of herself,
in what I thought

892
00:51:23,800 --> 00:51:25,166
was right for the character.

893
00:51:25,166 --> 00:51:26,400
But she didn't.

894
00:51:26,400 --> 00:51:28,934
And she came to me right before
we were all set up to shoot.

895
00:51:28,934 --> 00:51:32,133
And she said, I've been trying
this 100 different ways,

896
00:51:32,133 --> 00:51:34,300
and I have a feeling that
I'm going to commit myself

897
00:51:34,300 --> 00:51:37,066
on camera to something that
