00:52:23,300 --> 00:52:27,734
and this time I felt like it was
important to do it a little bit

915
00:52:27,734 --> 00:52:29,200
indirectly.

916
00:52:29,200 --> 00:52:32,033
So it's the scene
when she's having

917
00:52:32,033 --> 00:52:36,867
phone sex with Tony's character,
and her husband comes home.

918
00:52:36,867 --> 00:52:38,767
And she's really
freaked out about this,

919
00:52:38,767 --> 00:52:41,867
but she's even more freaked
out when Tony says to her,

920
00:52:41,867 --> 00:52:43,233
I know where you live.

921
00:52:43,233 --> 00:52:45,000
I peeled off the sticker.

