00:52:45,000 --> 00:52:47,967
And he's referring to
the return address that

923
00:52:47,967 --> 00:52:50,934
was on the envelope
that she sent him

924
00:52:50,934 --> 00:52:54,066
that she had covered up with
a sticker from her workplace.

925
00:52:54,066 --> 00:52:56,700
And I wanted Helen to have
a really big response,

926
00:52:56,700 --> 00:52:59,533
because it seemed like he was
almost threatening that he was

927
00:52:59,533 --> 00:53:03,300
going to break the
agreement they had

928
00:53:03,300 --> 00:53:05,767
to keep their lives separate,
which would have been really,

929
00:53:05,767 --> 00:53:07,300
really scary for
her at that time,

930
00:53:07,300 --> 00:53:08,934
especially because
