937
00:53:20,467 --> 00:53:24,066
And he said, well, I have
an idea that might help you,

938
00:53:24,066 --> 00:53:25,533
but you're going
to be on your own.

939
00:53:25,533 --> 00:53:27,667
I don't know how Helen
is going to react.

940
00:53:27,667 --> 00:53:32,166
And so what we worked out is
that without telling Helen,

941
00:53:32,166 --> 00:53:35,200
that when we shot the
scene in close-up,

942
00:53:35,200 --> 00:53:38,266
instead of saying the
lines as scripted,

943
00:53:38,266 --> 00:53:42,133
