at some point I had to let

1000
00:56:31,233 --> 00:56:32,967
go of some of the control.

1001
00:56:32,967 --> 00:56:36,700
So on the first day of shooting,
I gave my checkbook over to one

1002
00:56:36,700 --> 00:56:40,300
of the line producers,
