1003
00:56:40,300 --> 00:56:43,066
And after the second or
third day of shooting,

1004
00:56:43,066 --> 00:56:45,133
we sat down to see
how things were going.

1005
00:56:45,133 --> 00:56:47,367
And at that point
I found out that he

1006
00:56:47,367 --> 00:56:52,700
had spent the entire budget, not
just the budget for production,

1007
00:56:52,700 --> 00:56:57,200
but production and
post-production as well.

1008
00:56:57,200 --> 00:56:58,500
So I was a wreck.

1009
00:56:58,500 --> 00:56:59,734
I didn't know what to do.

