00:56:59,734 --> 00:57:04,166
And I was completely fried
from just the directing

1011
00:57:04,166 --> 00:57:06,967
responsibilities and couldn't
get to sleep that night,

1012
00:57:06,967 --> 00:57:09,233
and finally decided, OK,
